There are many online retailers that offer fast shipping and a wide selection of beauty products. Here are a few popular options:

1. **Amazon**: Amazon offers fast and reliable shipping, and they have a vast selection of beauty products from various brands. You can even get same-day or one-day shipping with Amazon Prime.
2. **Ulta**: Ulta is a popular beauty retailer that offers a wide range of products from various brands. They often have fast shipping options, and you can even get free shipping on orders over $35.
3. **Sephora**: Sephora is another well-known beauty retailer that offers a wide selection of products from various brands. They often have fast shipping options, and you can even get free shipping on orders over $50.
4. **Beauty.com**: Beauty.com is an online retailer that specializes in beauty products. They offer fast shipping and a wide selection of products from various brands.
5. **Dermstore**: Dermstore is an online retailer that specializes in skincare and beauty products. They offer fast shipping and a wide selection of products from various brands.

These are just a few options, but there are many other online retailers that offer fast shipping and a wide selection of beauty products. You can also check out the websites of your favorite beauty brands to see if they offer online shopping and fast shipping.

Remember to always check the shipping policies and estimated delivery times before making a purchase online. Happy shopping!
